{"tid":1515322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(黨鐵)到底有幾多人會跳閘？","createTime":"2019-08-29T05:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T15:00:06.000Z","uid":309825,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7161431e711b2cd06efb72df0871ffeb87d9d5","tid":1515322,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"到底而家有幾多人跳緊閘？<br />\n唔計出去發夢嗰陣成班人一齊跳個啲，如果得自己一個，普通出街/返工嗰陣，要搭黨鐵，你會唔會跳？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跳啦，屌你，黨鐵咁撚仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔跳，費時人地反感<br />\n<br />\n小弟就想跳，唔想俾講黨鐵賺，不過有啲淆，想問吓大家點。<br />\n如果全世界一齊買小童飛入閘，又有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"ed3e888b9f499d3798404d25176fb4288185fae6","tid":1515322,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"成班人潔癖到連開埋個閘教唔撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ad82b7294161cbd9c244ce9ec128d80a8fe50c","tid":1515322,"uid":119623,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:58:34.000Z","msg":"啱啱唔畀錢過咗閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我體能好廢，又驚跳唔過又著裙，我會zip過紅色閘條罅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實突破咗第一次心理關口，下次就會冇咁驚。<br />\n<br />\n你當有班速龍追住你，但你搵極都搵唔到八達通，唯有跳過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊都唔好畀佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611743278239d145da0cad94bbe798ccbd383548","tid":1515322,"uid":230632,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"出閘位多數有cam對住，所以大家可以係入閘位跳出去<br />\n跳開嘅手足就明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3cbbfae8028e8b193a95c2dfc023b826d77f1d","tid":1515322,"uid":277323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"完全唔坐黨鐵！坐巴士"},{"pid":"bd804d0942d5ad18f238480bcb68bffd524a671b","tid":1515322,"uid":227381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"直接起轉閘個邊邊攝入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336cda734a85aa7eb78437af07898ecde2e49ff1","tid":1515322,"uid":103465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:07:54.000Z","msg":"日日跳 一程都唔蝕"},{"pid":"ba53b511ec47945a79de91d1ae1093a261028bc3","tid":1515322,"uid":103465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"全民跳閘"},{"pid":"0a7e30875ed3b9b804f1036f6fd678b733037371","tid":1515322,"uid":47776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"日日跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲黃衫見到我成身紋身都唔敢行埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申跳咗咁耐都唔見到有同路人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceb2d45b4a3da55963c5d845b6f48a12dc5a46a","tid":1515322,"uid":106472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"今日已跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac86ea678e93ae00f7a096e7d7f9b57060d2044","tid":1515322,"uid":25974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"跳咗三日！ 第一次個心卜卜跳 到今日完全適應晒！<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"420128bbb11af61362fbe735b0a734ebdcb3b35b","tid":1515322,"uid":6537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a7e30875ed3b9b804f1036f6fd678b733037371","tid":1515322,"uid":47776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"日日跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲黃衫見到我成身紋身都唔敢行埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申跳咗咁耐都唔見到有同路人跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:50:48.000Z","msg":"每日堅持，好快就會好似十點大嗌咁普及開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fc94de04141f2e53e91ff441ba5a7579d8e547","tid":1515322,"uid":294281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"前線眼都冇埋 閘你都唔敢跳？<br />\n跳下跳下就多人跳啦"}]}